#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Odoo CRM** helps you organize your sales activities: track leads, close "
"opportunities and get accurate forecasts. Keep opportunities organized with "
"the pipeline and manage your day-to-day activities with meetings and next "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo CRM** vous aide Ă  organiser vos activitĂŠs de vente : suivez les "
"pistes, concluez les opportunitĂŠs et obtenez des prĂŠvisions prĂŠcises. Gardez "
"les opportunitĂŠs organisĂŠes grĂ˘ce au pipeline et gĂŠrez vos activitĂŠs "
"quotidiennes en utilisant les rĂŠunions et les prochaines activitĂŠs."

