"Pour consulter l'opportunitĂŠ nouvellement crĂŠĂŠe, accĂŠdez Ă  "
":menuselection:`CRM --> Mon pipeline`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:95
