"l'application **CRM**. Les partenaires revendeurs peuvent cliquer sur les "
"boutons :guilabel:`Je suis intĂŠressĂŠ` ou :guilabel:`Je ne suis pas "
"intĂŠressĂŠ`. Cliquer sur l'un de ces boutons affiche le formulaire "
":guilabel:`Retour sur l'opportunitĂŠ`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:None
msgid "The lead page as seen in a reseller's user portal."
msgstr ""
"Page de l'opportunitĂŠ telle qu'elle apparaĂŽt dans le portail utilisateur "
"d'un revendeur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:151
msgid ""
"If the partner has expressed interest, the form prompts them to enter their "
"next planned action and expected revenue for the lead and to confirm that "
"they have contacted the customer. Entering this information and clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button converts the lead into an opportunity. "
"Failing to fill out the form **prevents** the lead from converting to an "
"opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Si le partenaire a exprimĂŠ son intĂŠrĂŞt, le formulaire l'invite Ă  saisir sa "
"prochaine action planifiĂŠe et le revenu attendu pour l'opportunitĂŠ et Ă  "
"confirmer qu'il a contactĂŠ le client. Saisir ces informations et cliquer sur "
"le bouton :guilabel:`Confirmer` convertit l'opportunitĂŠ en opportunitĂŠ. Ne "
"pas remplir le formulaire **empĂŞche** la conversion de l'opportunitĂŠ en "
"opportunitĂŠ."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Lead Feedback form brought up by clicking the \"I'm interested\" button."
msgstr ""
"Formulaire Retour sur l'opportunitĂŠ affichĂŠ en cliquant sur le bouton \"Je "
"suis intĂŠressĂŠ\"."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:159
