#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:3
msgid "Commissions"
msgstr "Commissions"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:7
msgid ""
"Commissions are a powerful tool to motivate sales team members. They "
"incentivize performance, boost productivity, and encourage healthy "
"competition. The *Commissions* feature in Odoo's **Sales** application "
"provides a way to reward salespeople or sales teams based on their "
"performance. This feature supports the creation of flexible, measurable "
"commission structures that align with business goals, whether that means "
"driving revenue, volume, profit, or recurring contracts."
msgstr ""
"Les commissions constituent un outil puissant pour motiver les membres d'une "
"ĂŠquipe commerciale. Elles encouragent la performance, stimulent la "
"productivitĂŠ et favorisent une concurrence saine. La fonctionnalitĂŠ "
"*Commissions* de l'application **Ventes** d'Odoo permet de rĂŠcompenser les "
"commerciaux ou les ĂŠquipes commerciales en fonction de leurs performances. "
"Cette fonctionnalitĂŠ prend en charge la crĂŠation de structures de "
"commissions flexibles et mesurables qui s'alignent sur les objectifs "
"commerciaux, qu'il s'agisse de gĂŠnĂŠrer du chiffre d'affaires, du volume, du "
"profit ou des contrats rĂŠcurrents."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:16
msgid ""
"To enable the *Commissions* feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. Scroll to the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, "
"and tick the :guilabel:`Commissions` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"Doing so causes a new :guilabel:`Commissions` menu to appear in the menu "
"bar. To create a new commission plan, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Commissions --> Comission Plans` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer la fonctionnalitĂŠ *Commissions*, aller Ă  "
":menuselection:`application Ventes --> Configuration --> ParamĂ¨tres`. Faire "
"dĂŠfiler jusqu'Ă  la section :guilabel:`Facturation` et cocher la case "
":guilabel:`Commissions`. Cliquer ensuite sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`. Un "
"nouveau menu :guilabel:`Commissions` apparaĂŽt alors dans la barre de menus. "
"Pour crĂŠer un nouveau plan de commissions, aller Ă  "
":menuselection:`Commissions --> Plans de commissions` et cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:23
msgid "Commission plan structure"
msgstr "Structure du plan de commissions"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:25
msgid "Each commission plan is comprised of several components:"
msgstr "Chaque plan de commissions comprend plusieurs composants :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:27
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Based on`: Determines whether commissions are awarded based on "
"progress toward :guilabel:`Targets` or :guilabel:`Achievements`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`BasĂŠ sur` : dĂŠtermine si les commissions sont attribuĂŠes en "
"fonction de la progression vers des :guilabel:`objectifs` ou des "
":guilabel:`rĂŠalisations`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`per`: Indicates whether the plan applies to individual "
"salespeople or an entire sales team"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`par` : indique si le plan s'applique Ă  des commerciaux "
"individuels ou Ă  une ĂŠquipe commerciale entiĂ¨re"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Target Frequency`: Sets how often targets reset: **Monthly**, "
"**Quarterly**, or **Yearly**."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`FrĂŠquence des objectifs` : dĂŠfinit la frĂŠquence de "
"rĂŠinitialisation des objectifs : **mensuelle**, **trimestrielle** ou "
"**annuelle**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Achievements`: Determines what is being measured toward "
"commissions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`RĂŠalisations` : dĂŠtermine ce qui est mesurĂŠ pour les commissions."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:None
msgid "A new commission plan detail form."
msgstr "Un nouveau formulaire dĂŠtaillĂŠ de plan de commissions."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:39
msgid "Target-based commission plans"
msgstr "Plans de commissions basĂŠs sur des objectifs"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:41
msgid ""
"In a *Target* based commission plan, commissions are awarded based on the "
"percentage of sales targets reached. Target based plans are ideal for "
"setting clear, measurable goals, such as invoicing a specific amount in "
"sales per quarter, then rewarding sales people progressively based on how "
"close they come to reaching or exceeding that goal."
msgstr ""
"Dans un plan de commissions basĂŠ sur des *objectifs*, les commissions sont "
"attribuĂŠes en fonction du pourcentage d'objectifs de vente atteints. Les "
"plans basĂŠs sur des objectifs sont idĂŠaux pour dĂŠfinir des objectifs clairs "
"et mesurables, comme facturer un montant spĂŠcifique de ventes par trimestre, "
"puis rĂŠcompenser progressivement les commerciaux en fonction de leur "
"proximitĂŠ avec l'atteinte ou le dĂŠpassement de cet objectif."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:47
msgid ""
"Target based plans differ from *Achievement* based plans because they are "
"based on reaching a fixed, predefined goal. They focus on goal-based "
"incentives and performance milestones."
msgstr ""
"Les plans basĂŠs sur des objectifs diffĂ¨rent des plans basĂŠs sur des "
"*rĂŠalisations* car ils reposent sur l'atteinte d'un objectif fixe et "
"prĂŠdĂŠfini. Ils se concentrent sur des incitations basĂŠes sur des objectifs "
"et des jalons de performance."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/commissions.rst:50
