msgstr ""
"Le champ :guilabel:`Distribution analytique` proposera **uniquement** la "
"commande correspondante en tant qu'option si la commande contient un produit "
"de service dont la facturation est basĂŠe sur les *Feuilles de temps*, les "
"*Jalons* ou la *QuantitĂŠ livrĂŠe*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to properly fill out an expense form that's attached to a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Comment correctement remplir une note de frais qui est liĂŠe Ă  une commande "
"dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:215
msgid ""
"If there are any receipts that should be uploaded and attached to the "
"expense, click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and upload the "
