":guilabel:`Configurer les champs dynamiques`. Pour plus de dĂŠtails, "
"consulter :doc:`pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:92
msgid ""
