"l'onglet :guilabel:`GĂŠnĂŠrateur de devis`, :guilabel:`Ajouter` ou "
":guilabel:`TĂŠlĂŠcharger` un PDF directement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:103
