"Shopee, et sĂŠlectionner :guilabel:`DĂŠpĂ´t groupĂŠ` comme :guilabel:`Mode de "
"paiement`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:170
msgid ""
"This same action can be performed with vendor bills from Shopee dedicated to "
"fees/commissions."
msgstr ""
"Cette mĂŞme action peut ĂŞtre effectuĂŠe avec les factures fournisseur de "
"Shopee dĂŠdiĂŠes aux frais/commissions."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:172
